       01 EKRAN-2.
           05 BLANK SCREEN.
           05 LINE 1 COLUMN 1 VALUE "BEBIM A.S.".
           05 LINE 5 COLUMN 15 VALUE "CARI HESAP PROGRAMI".
           05 LINE 6 COLUMN 15 PIC X(37) FROM ALL "=".
           05 LINE 7 COLUMN 15 VALUE "[1]:CARI MIZAN PROGRAMI".
